{"tid":233394,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"當年同謝小姐講分手，但係要我比錢佢食野","createTime":"2017-05-07T13:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T18:59:39.000Z","uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5e1df142e4962737825fb7a7cb9e217f466d57","tid":233394,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"中四識咗謝小姐，一直到中六都好恩愛<br />\n但係中六之後都差唔多放榜，其實都預咗 Come on James<br />\n就係放榜前兩個月，我同佢講分手(話曬我都係未來Kong U仔)<br />\n<br />\n謝小姐：搵間餐廳再傾啦六常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n六常：我對住你冇胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n謝小姐：咁你比$500我搵餐廳食野啦咁<br />\n六常：Cls ，你食野自己埋單啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔咗冇耐之後佢唱到我通街都係，說甚麼「唔比錢唔合作」「同你一齊咁耐，請佢食餐飯或者送記念品好應該」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/214851_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F214851_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=42a44bd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47230f08bec685e7c2b0398860c66c20c0fc503b","tid":233394,"uid":17881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"佢都講得啱嘅"},{"pid":"04d61864dc23791bb41d7a3679a39eecc67e725c","tid":233394,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢都講得啱嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明點解件事通曬街仲咁多人撐謝小姐"},{"pid":"e220a43c064e61649fd38a581fb5bb0fbaa27b9d","tid":233394,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"謝絲燕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df3e385e500a30e6bee3a2bd74c00c5fdf524b5","tid":233394,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝絲燕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></b